Customize Chat Window Branding for a Experience Site

Select the chat window colors and font to reflect your companyâ€™s brand identity on an Experience Cloud site.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Embedded Service setup node is available in: Lightning Experience
Available in: Essentials, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

To customize chat window branding colors, images, and fonts on an Experience site, use the settings in the Embedded Chat component.

From the Experience Builder make sure that your chat window is selected. Navigate to the Theme tab.
Select the colors for your chat window.
Select your font and add images to your chat window:
Agent Avatar
Logo
Pre-Chat Background
Waiting State

Save your site.
These branding tokens are created in Embedded Service Setup and automatically pass to your site: width, height, header text, and header alternate.

General Embedded Service Branding
title: Customizing Chat Window Branding for Experience Site
